    "description": "《Make It Count》是一款 1-3 名玩家合作、后世界末日、自上而下的射击游戏，带有 Roguelite 元素。<br>作为人类最后的幸存者，你有责任消灭地球上这些肮脏的生物。开始任务并通过寻找各种饰品变得更加强大！收集有意义的资源来解锁、升级武器和角色。消灭这些可恶的生物，满足你的嗜血欲望！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>MAKE IT COUNT</li></ul></strong><br>Make It Count 中的弹药是有限的，它并不稀缺，但你必须让你的射击有价值！在任务中搜刮弹药和其他有用的东西是必须的！或者，您也可以掏出近战武器大开杀戒！<br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>任务</li></ul></strong><br>每次运行都可能会出现不同的路径！路线是随机的，不是无限的，但会为游戏中的不同迷你任务和饰品提供多样性！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/596a57ca6c56c0cabda332de43e664bf.poster.avif?t=1753107284\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/596a57ca6c56c0cabda332de43e664bf.webm?t=1753107284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>战争迷雾</li></ul></strong><br>要小心！你的视野有限，危险无处不在！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/dee718849f4f051f8f57ec78b0bb500c.poster.avif?t=1753107284\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/dee718849f4f051f8f57ec78b0bb500c.webm?t=1753107284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>个性化</li></ul></strong><br>在您的 HUB 区域休闲时，您可以升级武器和角色。这还不是全部！您还可以在您的 HUB 中制作各种装饰品，使其在视觉上更吸引您的眼球！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/312ade6b8eca6434e63b488e0c605212.poster.avif?t=1753107284\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126220/extras/312ade6b8eca6434e63b488e0c605212.webm?t=1753107284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
